{"id": 2848, "genre": 1001, "title": "如今做什么事会让你觉得时间被按了快进键？", "description": "人生最危险的事，莫过于把闹钟关掉后又闭上了眼睛。（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ istock）", "record_count": 2353, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190325121506mbsc1LMin5kAGyVa.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-25T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 333568, "content": "看《权力的游戏》总会觉得“怎么就完了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335360, "content": "打开steam", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541847}, {"id": 333569, "content": "每一个深夜“最后再玩一局”的那一局", "image": null, "praise_count": 121, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335363, "content": "看历史通史？或者去历史博物馆参观？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541847}, {"id": 335364, "content": "做自己热爱的事时", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618386}, {"id": 335620, "content": "玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619111}, {"id": 335365, "content": "虚度光阴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390776}, {"id": 335621, "content": "每一个工作日的早晨，做啥啥都快", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404895}, {"id": 335622, "content": "物理卷子永远写不完的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607265}, {"id": 335367, "content": "周末", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511660}, {"id": 335623, "content": "每当要考试的时候，时间总是过得很快！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614864}, {"id": 335879, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/2019032712121312VIPQk07e8Gh4tH", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620566}, {"id": 335368, "content": "大概是上学的时候？\n一周里每天都觉得难捱\n但是回过头来一看突然发现时间都不见了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1610735}, {"id": 335624, "content": "刷手机啊！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607265}, {"id": 335625, "content": "昏睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619144}, {"id": 335370, "content": "满是计划的一星期", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103270}, {"id": 335626, "content": "学习和考试", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619145}, {"id": 335882, "content": "初三的最后一个学期", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619552}, {"id": 335371, "content": "撸猫", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512341}, {"id": 335372, "content": "假期和周末。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618417}, {"id": 335629, "content": "打怪猎的时候，几只龙下来咋就十二点了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619177}, {"id": 335630, "content": "玩手机、追番、玩游戏还有睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619106}, {"id": 343566, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 336143, "content": "清晨醒来才6点，想再多睡一会，一闭眼一睁眼已经8点半了！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498015}, {"id": 335633, "content": "工作的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619204}, {"id": 335890, "content": "和朋友谈心的时候，说不完的话总会因为时间太快而意犹未尽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1520615}, {"id": 335635, "content": "如今不管做什么都觉得时间特别快 眨一下眼一天就过去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615126}, {"id": 335380, "content": "晚上看单词的时候，啊，一天又过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456839}, {"id": 335381, "content": "当然是补剧 日出而作日落而息π_π", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500115}, {"id": 335637, "content": "看小说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619210}, {"id": 335382, "content": "假期最后一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570759}, {"id": 335638, "content": "打游戏的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618203}, {"id": 335383, "content": "看手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064367}, {"id": 335639, "content": "临时抱佛脚的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618203}, {"id": 335384, "content": "进行一项需要反复修改的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590515}, {"id": 335640, "content": "打开微博或者随便一个对我来说意味着娱乐的app", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247584}, {"id": 335386, "content": "做手工做手工呀", "image": "img/option/option/20190325155650AFrzMlhEXsSnjcG3.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618433}, {"id": 335387, "content": "逝去的时间会想起来都过得很快，所以，大概就是回想过去的时间的时候一瞬间感觉自己的时间被按了加速键，而加速度的大小取决于我们回想起了多久以前。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618426}, {"id": 335388, "content": "日复一日，年复一年！不变的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450453}, {"id": 335389, "content": "上学", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618438}, {"id": 335391, "content": "写论文拿起手机的瞬间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618442}, {"id": 335392, "content": "看美妆、生活分享类vlog", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515073}, {"id": 335648, "content": "练琴的时光快乐而短暂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 335393, "content": "忙完了一天，回家吃完饭打扫完健完身，总有那么两个小时能够干一点很喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1539815}, {"id": 335649, "content": "分手的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619241}, {"id": 335394, "content": "逛淘宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600473}, {"id": 335395, "content": "去喜欢的国家度假", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585863}, {"id": 335396, "content": "早上第一次睁眼和闭眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615830}, {"id": 335397, "content": "睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611597}, {"id": 335400, "content": "每个项目最后时间节点的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479450}]}